title: Check service availability
description: To check the availability of the service, enter the Discord server ID or its name in the field below (case-insensitive). The default setting searches for all bots offered by the application. To narrow down the results, select one of the JWizard applications from the list.
disclaimerInfo: If the feedback message shows that the service is available on the selected server but is still not working, please report it to the following address:
isAvailable: Service in searched Discord guild is available.
isUnavailable: Service is searched Discord guild is unavailable.
